creator: DICE
descriptionHtml:
DICE has the shows you want to go to, in real life and online. Spanning music, arts and culture, we have hundreds of choice events happening every day, but we’ll only recommend shows we know you’ll love.

With DICE, you can:

•  stream shows, festivals and workshops from all around the world
•  get tickets to live events in London, Paris, Milan, Barcelona, Madrid, Los Angeles and New York when we’re able to go out again
•  invite friends, follow each other, and get suggestions for shows that you’ll both like and can attend together
•  sync your Spotify or Apple Music and receive personalised recommendations based on your music library
•  save events for later and we’ll let you know if tickets are running low closer to the date, or get reminders for when events go on sale so you don’t miss out
•  join a waiting list if an event’s sold out and be next in line to get tickets, or get a refund if you can no longer go
•  transfer tickets to a friend if you have a spare, can’t make it or as a gift because you’re nice like that.

If you have any questions, feelings, concerns, or just want to say hi – send an email to help@dice.fm.
descriptionShort: DICE lets you discover the best events and live streams.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
You'll be happy to know you can now follow your favourite artists. By doing so we'll notify you when they're doing a gig, so you don't miss out on seeing them.

And if you come across an event where you don't know the support act or someone on the line-up, jumping to their artist profile will give you a better idea of who they are and what to expect.

title: DICE: Live Shows

creator: DICE FM
descriptionHtml:
Live shows make us feel good. They’re a time to hang with our friends, discover new artists or lose ourselves on a dancefloor. We’re on a mission to bring all of this to more fans, more often. Download DICE to see what’s happening in your city.

With DICE, you can:
•  sync your Spotify or Apple Music and receive personalised recommendations based on your music library
•  get tickets to live shows from all around the world
•  invite friends, follow each other, and get suggestions for shows that you’ll both like and can attend together
•  save events for later and find out if tickets are running low closer to the date, or get reminders for when they’re on sale so you don’t miss out
•  join the Waiting List for sold-out events and be next in line to get tickets, or get a refund if you can no longer go
•  transfer tickets to a friend if you have a spare, can’t make it or as a gift because you’re nice like that.

If you have any questions, feelings, concerns, or just want to say hi – send an email to help@dice.fm.

•  invite friends, follow each other, and get suggestions for shows that you’ll both like and can attend together
•  save events for later and find out if tickets are running low closer to the date, or get reminders for when they’re on sale so you don’t miss out
•  join the Waiting List for sold-out events and be next in line to get tickets, or get a refund if you can no longer go
•  transfer tickets to a friend if you have a spare, can’t make it or as a gift because you’re nice like that.

If you have any questions, feelings, concerns, or just want to say hi – send an email to help@dice.fm.

creator: DICE FM
descriptionHtml:
DICE has the shows you want to go to, in real life and online. Spanning music, arts and culture, we have hundreds of choice events happening every day, but we’ll only recommend shows we know you’ll love.

With DICE, you can:

•  stream shows, festivals and workshops from all around the world
•  get tickets to live events in London, Paris, Milan, Barcelona, Madrid, Los Angeles and New York when we’re able to go out again
•  invite friends, follow each other, and get suggestions for shows that you’ll both like and can attend together
•  sync your music streaming app and receive personalised recommendations based on your music library
•  save events for later and we’ll let you know if tickets are running low closer to the date, or get reminders for when events go on sale so you don’t miss out
•  join a waiting list if an event’s sold out and be next in line to get tickets, or get a refund if you can no longer go
•  transfer tickets to a friend if you have a spare, can’t make it or as a gift because you’re nice like that.

If you have any questions, feelings, concerns, or just want to say hi – send an email to help@dice.fm.

title: DICE: Live Shows

creator: DICE FM
descriptionHtml:
Live shows make us feel good. They’re a time to hang with our friends, discover new artists or lose ourselves on a dancefloor. We’re on a mission to bring all of this to more fans, more often. Download DICE to see what’s happening in your city.

With DICE, you can:
•  sync your Spotify or Apple Music and receive personalised recommendations based on your music library
•  get tickets to live shows from all around the world
•  invite friends, follow each other, and get suggestions for shows that you’ll both like and can attend together
•  save events for later and find out if tickets are running low closer to the date, or get reminders for when they’re on sale so you don’t miss out
•  join the Waiting List for sold-out events and be next in line to get tickets, or get a refund if you can no longer go
•  transfer tickets to a friend if you have a spare, can’t make it or as a gift because you’re nice like that.

If you have any questions, feelings, concerns, or just want to say hi – send an email to help@dice.fm.

title: DICE: Live Shows

creator: DICE FM
descriptionHtml:
Live shows make us feel good.

That’s true whether you’re looking for basement gigs or club nights, massive festivals or comedy shows.

DICE’s personalised recommendations make it easy for you to enjoy more of the events you love – wherever you are, whatever you’re into.

Download DICE to see what’s happening in your city.

Why DICE?

Discover live events tailored to your tastes.

Get tickets to shows in your city, and around the world.

Connect your Spotify or Apple Music to see suggestions based on your music library.

Follow your favourite artists and venues, and be the first to hear about new shows.

Invite friends, follow each other and get suggestions for shows you can enjoy together.

Save events for later, set reminders for when tickets go on sale, and check if tickets are running low.

Join the Waiting List for sold-out events to get your hands on tickets, or offer yours to the queue if you can no longer attend.

Send tickets to a friend if you have a spare, can’t make it or as a gift – because you’re nice like that.

If you have any questions, feelings, concerns, or just want to say hi – send an email to help@dice.fm.

Plus, you’ll get recommendations based on everyone’s saved events. Start planning your next night out on DICE – your friends will thank you.

title: DICE: Live Shows

creator: DICE FM
descriptionHtml:
Live shows make us feel good.

That’s true whether you’re looking for basement gigs or club nights, massive festivals or comedy shows.

DICE’s personalised recommendations make it easy for you to enjoy more of the events you love – wherever you are, whatever you’re into.

Download DICE to see what’s happening in your city.

Why DICE?

Discover live events tailored to your tastes.

Get tickets to shows in your city, and around the world.

Connect your Spotify or Apple Music to see suggestions based on your music library.

Follow your favourite artists and venues, and be the first to hear about new shows.

Invite friends, follow each other and get suggestions for shows you can enjoy together.

Save events for later, set reminders for when tickets go on sale, and check if tickets are running low.

Join the Waiting List for sold-out events to get your hands on tickets, or offer yours to the queue if you can no longer attend.

Send tickets to a friend if you have a spare, can’t make it or as a gift – because you’re nice like that.

If you have any questions, feelings, concerns, or just want to say hi – send an email to help@dice.fm.

That’s true whether you’re looking for basement gigs or club nights, massive festivals or comedy shows.

DICE’s personalised recommendations make it easy for you to enjoy more of the events you love – wherever you are, whatever you’re into.

Download DICE to see what’s happening in your city.

Why DICE?

Discover live events tailored to your tastes.

Get tickets to shows in your city, and around the world.

Connect your Spotify or Apple Music to see suggestions based on your music library.

Follow your favourite artists and venues, and be the first to hear about new shows.

Invite friends, follow each other and get suggestions for shows you can enjoy together.

Save events for later, set reminders for when tickets go on sale, and check if tickets are running low.

Join the Waiting List for sold-out events to get your hands on tickets, or offer yours to the queue if you can no longer attend.

Send tickets to a friend if you have a spare, can’t make it or as a gift – because you’re nice like that.

If you have any questions, feelings, concerns, or just want to say hi – send an email to help@dice.fm.
descriptionShort: Discover events from around the world

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Change of plans? We got you. Now if you put your tickets up for sale on the Waiting List but later decide you want to use them, you can get them back.
